embeds.description: 9 votes and 6 comments so far on Reddit

messages.content:
I was struggling with the same issue and here is what I found that worked:

    Go to File -> Options -> Customize Ribbon

    There should be two columns: "Choose commands from:" on the left and "Customize the Ribbon:" on the right.

    Under "Customize the Ribbon:", go to the "Draw" section and then click the "New Group" button down at the bottom of the window. You can name it something like "Pan".

    Under "Choose commands from:", choose "All Commands" from the drop down menu instead of "Popular Commands".

    Scroll through the (now really long) list of commands until you find the "Panning Hand" command.

    Select the "Panning Hand" command and make sure the New Group you just made (which I called "Pan") is selected on the right, then click the "Add >> " button in the middle.
